   <div class="hero__home" style="background-image: url('/media/homepage-stories/Blanchard-Hall-in-Snow.jpg')">
    <div class="hero__home__wrap">
     <div class="hero__home__header">
      From Wheaton to the World
     </div>
     <div class="hero__home__content">
      <p>
       As the top distinctively Christian liberal arts college in the U.S., Wheaton College ranks among the best liberal arts colleges in the nation according to
       <em>
        U.S. News &amp; World Report, Forbes, Kiplinger’s
       </em>
       , and
       <em>
        Fiske
       </em>
       . Wheaton offers an affordable top-tier education that will prepare you to make an impact in the world for Christ and his Kingdom.
       <a href="https://www.wheaton.edu/admissions-and-aid/apply-to-wheaton-college/">
        <span style="color: white; text-decoration: underline;">
         <strong>
          Apply Today.
         </strong>
        </span>
       </a>
      </p>
      <button class="hero__home__button">
