           Student Profile
          </a>
          <p class="p--large">
           Ben Kubacki '19 grew up appreciating the simplicity of small communities in Brazil and Angola as a missionary kid. Now, as a student at Wheaton, he is drawn to the complexities of environmental science and urban studies. Ben hopes to apply his passion for global wholeness in an urban community development setting.
